      &lt;img alt="Vector illustration of the xAI logo." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wwdU-3L8GszcO0wNjWxT81f2nWg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73751837/STK262_GROK_XAI__A.0.png" /&gt;
